    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I'm Peri. P as in pierce! E as in eviscerate! R as in rupture! And what's the I for...? Injure! I'm a cavalier from Nohr, so just point me in a direction and I'll get stabby!",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "The commander is pretty. How does she get her hair so red? Maybe with the blood of her enemies!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Lord Xander is my liege. He can be a little scary, but I like him anyway. He lets me fight lots and lots!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Good work patrolling. Hey, if you get tired, come to me for some huggy, squeezy, head-patty friend time!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I make a great stew. First, I go to a good butcher. Then I look for fresh, red meat—the drippier, the better!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I think about my mommy a lot. She's gone, forever. But I'm a good cook like she was, so she'll live forever!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Ooooh! I found you! I found you! You've got to be <Player Name>, right? Someone friendly-wendly sent me here to say hi. It was <Friend Name>!",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "Great! Can I go back to killing guys now?",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Let's see what color bad-guy blood is!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Ugh! That's almost nothing!",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "You made me stronger, so I'll get stabby with anyone you want!",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "Oh, I've been looking for you. I have something tasty-wasty that I made for you! Cooked it myself. Oh, and I sliced and diced the meat—and all the veggies too! Eat up while it's hot. Like it? Scrumptious, right? YAY! My mommy was great at cooking. That's why I want to be good at it too. That way, it's like she's with me! More than anything, it means that I know how to make you happy-wappy! So, count on Peri to spice things up in the battle AND the kitchen from now on!",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
